  <brief_title>Nasya in Allergic Rhinitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Crossover Clinical Investigation to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of Nasya in Reducing Symptoms of Allergic Rhinitis When Applied Before Allergen Challenge</official_title>
  <sponsors>
