  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  History of persistent allergic rhinitis due to house dust mite allergy ≥ 2 years

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinically significant disease that could interfere with the evaluation of study
             medication

          -  Participation in other studies within the last 4 weeks / during the study
